{"tid":1172342,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被fd zone了仲可以點","createTime":"2019-05-26T11:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T15:05:48.000Z","uid":249454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"567a1ceb356477bd12d61a217215d096615be11e","tid":1172342,"uid":249454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"利申 巴打<br />\n因為有共同朋友 連續兩年都同到女神去旅行<br />\n上年佢應該feel到我鐘意佢<br />\n因為我講過俾我地既共同朋友知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且旅行都有搭住佢影相<br />\n但佢都冇咩反應<br />\n然後自己又細膽<br />\n不了了之左<br />\n但一直都有用朋友mode咁間唔中傾下同食下飯<br />\n呢排見多左 又勾番起對佢既情感<br />\n同佢一齊真係好舒服好開心<br />\n想問下各位咁樣可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到既話 比次機會比大家試下好冇"},{"pid":"a72b8faff4019bda70aa831597fa765b2f4507d9","tid":1172342,"uid":61018,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"搵個另一個啦"},{"pid":"2c85fd738090bef98fd5585e31a03568986e7a7b","tid":1172342,"uid":218407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"冇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走啦唔好再浪費自己時間"},{"pid":"3d5233c6305e0dc9a9569ab900a49c09344995b6","tid":1172342,"uid":249454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"識佢呢幾年 佢都冇拍拖<br />\n成日覺得仲有d機會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451a1f099342d2175b211298f576fea984329b54","tid":1172342,"uid":253512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"抱住必死既心態表白<br />\n得米就得<br />\n唔得就斬纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}